{"tid":2516303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日見到港鐵職員唔比兩個無拆 前碌既單車乘客搭,真係好on9","createTime":"2021-05-04T14:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T14:45:06.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"179315ab7a59712da9c22a5006ca1e635eadc6cd","tid":2516303,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"話說今日收工果陣, 見到兩個後生仔 推住單車入港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n跟住突然幾個港鐵職員 如臨大敵咁衝過去, 要求佢地架單車拆前碌<br />\n點知佢地架單車原來拆唔到前碌, 跟住港鐵職員就叫佢地離開<br />\n<br />\n真係好on9, 點解要拆前碌?? 唔拆又阻唔到幾多位置<br />\n睇到我堅係嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4a1efaa317d11c7d2960fcd6f4137d30ac5e5f","tid":2516303,"uid":155431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"1.規矩<br />\n2.撞到我點算<br />\n3.踩返屋企啦"},{"pid":"efb84cddd128e3dad697c29f48e2b0e94e4c624d","tid":2516303,"uid":136797,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"有單車點解搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ce0d543b330b125d7bd87168c916e5a64247a4","tid":2516303,"uid":25520,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"efb84cddd128e3dad697c29f48e2b0e94e4c624d","tid":2516303,"uid":136797,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"有單車點解搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"你有腳點解要搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395029c42a66aa3cb21b2c9d68ae55c2d9814186","tid":2516303,"uid":98358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"唔係摺車，好似寫明要拆"},{"pid":"7e02d3